Beáta Dei Génitrix, María, * Virgo perpétua, templum Dómini, sacrárium Spíritus Sancti, sola sine exémplo placuísti Dómino nostro Jesu Christo, allelúja.
O blessed Mary, Mother of God, * ever a Virgin, temple of the Lord, sanctuary of the Holy Ghost, thou alone without example didst please our Lord Jesus Christ, alleluia.
